                         option(value='M1a',title='Separate tumour nodule(s) in a contralateral lobe tumour with pleural nodes or malignant pleural (or pericardial) effusion') #{ __('Separate tumour nodule(s) in a contralateral lobe tumour with pleural nodes or malignant pleural (or pericardial) effusion') }
                         option(value='M1b',title='Distant metastases') #{ __('Distant metastases') }
                      span(onclick='resetDistantM()')
                        | Reset
